  "texts": [
    "Active learning, multitask learning, one-shot learning, federated learning (a sort of ML in which the model is trained by utilizing separate private data held in multiple places without sacrificing data privacy), etc., are many other methods (other than transfer learning and data augmentation) that may be used to make the most of the insufficient data.",
    "The originality and reliability of the resulting molecule from GAI are affected by several variables, including the nature of the data and the GAI model used.",
