    "Evaluating GAI models and the quality of their output is often more difficult and time-consuming than AI-based predictive models.",
    "This is because GAI tools sometimes need users to prioritize competing goals simultaneously (such as increasing the resemblance to known bioactive compounds while simultaneously increasing structural uniqueness)."
